Privacy Policy for rdcalculator

At rdcalculator, accessible from the Google Play Store, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our users, especially minors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by rdcalculator and how we use it.

If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us through email at lyx668@outlook.com.

Information Collection and Use

rdcalculator does not collect any personal information from its users. The app does not require internet access and does not collect any user data or messages.

Log Data

We do not collect any log data from our users.

Cookies

rdcalculator does not use cookies.

Children's Information

We believe it is important to provide added protection for children online. We encourage parents and guardians to spend time online with their children to observe, participate in and/or monitor and guide their online activity.

rdcalculator does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable Information from children under the age of 13. If you think that your child provided this kind of information on our app, we strongly encourage you to contact us immediately and we will do our best efforts to promptly remove such information from our records.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, we advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at lyx668@outlook.com.
